{
  "stem": "26142.15",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would go out-- this was already-- this was already in-- in in October, November-- we were going out in the evening when it-- it's dark.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It took us an hour to get there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they had some little-- little bridges that they made and-- and boats to get to that island.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very easy to dig in that, because it was just purely sand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- when it was wet and raining in-- in October, November time, you were going in the water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was nowhere where you could sit down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that place, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were also so disgusted with that work that we didn't-- we were going-- they-- they ordered us to go in a single line because it's safer to go on a single line than on-- in three abreast or four abreast that normally units go.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you could hear the-- the-- the swishes of the-- of the bullets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for some reason, we didn't-- we didn't we didn't fear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had no fear because it-- it was such miserable life that we didn't-- we didn't fear anymore-- anymore whatever happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway we worked there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] till sometimes-- till sometimes in December.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then in December-- there-- yeah, I-- I have to-- I have to mention this here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From our group, there was one boy that was from Romania.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He spoke Romanian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In one of the [NON-ENGLISH], one of the-- of the Hungarian soldiers-- he was a-- from Romania.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a mixture somehow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was all-- all there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they-- they were able to speak Romanian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They talked together that they would desert.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But you couldn't swim that river over because it's a huge river.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
